        df_len = pd.DataFrame(df.groupby(1)[8].agg('median'))
        df_len.columns = [file]
        df_concat = pd.concat([df_concat,df_len],axis=1)

plt.figure(figsize=(24,12))
for i,tissue in enumerate(tissues):
    polyA = tissue + "_polyA"
    corr_tissue = df_corr[[tissue,polyA]].dropna()
    corr_tissue[tissue] = np.log10(corr_tissue[tissue])
    corr_tissue = corr_tissue.query(f'{tissue}>1')
    corr_val = round(corr_tissue.corr().iloc[0,1],2)
    plt.subplot(2,4,i+1)
    sns.regplot(data = corr_tissue,x=tissue,y=polyA,ci=0,color=OkabeIto().colors[6],scatter_kws={"s":12,"color": OkabeIto().colors[2] })
    plt.ylim(0,200)
    plt.text(3.5,175, f'Pearson R={corr_val}', ha='center', va='bottom')
    plt.title(tissue)
    break
